  <brief_title>Effects of Long Biliopancreatic Limb vs. Long Alimentary Limb in Superobesity, a Randomized Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Study Comparing the Effects of Gastric Bypass Using a Long BP-limb vs. a Long Alimentary Limb in Morbid Obesity</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Aleris Obesity</agency>
